---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import KitForm from '../components/KitForm';
---

<Layout
  description="Weekly reflections on human skills in tech, from developer to tech lead to architect. 25+ years of lessons on working better and happier."
>
  <div class="page home-page">
    <section class="intro">
      <h1>Humanity matters.</h1>

      <p class="tagline">
        We need uniquely human skills and better ways of working more than ever.
      </p>

      <p class="emphasis">
        Developers: the human skills many of us have been taught to ignore or dismiss as "soft
        skills" are essential tools for doing excellent technical work and avoiding burnout,
        plateaus, and isolation.
      </p>

      <p>
        Building trust and influence. Handling complexity and ambiguity. Systems thinking.
        Intuition and judgment based on experience. Collaboration and communication. Empathy.
        Creativity.
      </p>

      <p>
        Hi, I'm Leaf. Over the past 25 years, as I've progressed from developer to tech lead and
        application architect, the skills I've needed have increasingly been about more than just
        writing code. I'm <strong
          >now writing a <a href="/book">book</a></strong
        > about how our humanity helps us thrive as developers, teams, and organizations.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="cta">
      <p>
        <b>Come join me on this adventure.</b> Sign up to receive weekly reflections on working better
        and happier and why humanity matters in tech:
      </p>

      <KitForm formId="c29f7b6897" className="home-signup-form" client:load />

      <p class="additional-channels">
        You can also find my writing here in <a href="/posts">my blog posts</a>, which also appear
        on <a
          href="https://www.linkedin.com/newsletters/beyond-writing-code-7394107177700970497"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a
        >, <a href="https://bouncingleaf.medium.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >Medium</a
        >, <a href="https://bouncingleaf.substack.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >Substack</a
        >, and <a
          href="https://bsky.app/profile/leafjessicaroy.bsky.social"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer">Bluesky</a
        >. You can also find me on <a
          href="https://www.instagram.com/leafjessicaroy/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer">Instagram</a
        >.
      </p>

      <p>Glad you're here!</p>

      <p class="hidden-verification">
        Oh yeah, I'm also on <a
          href="https://hachyderm.io/@leafjessicaroy"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer">Mastodon</a
        >.
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page {
    max-width: var(--content-max-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: var(--spacing-lg) 0;
  }

  .home-page .intro {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);
  }

  .home-page h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .tagline {
    font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 2vw, 1.5rem);
    font-weight: 500;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
    color: var(--color-accent-teal);
  }

  .emphasis {
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .home-page p {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .cta {
    background-color: var(--color-light-cream);
    padding: var(--spacing-lg);
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-top: var(--spacing-xl);
  }

  .additional-channels {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    margin-top: var(--spacing-lg);
  }

  .hidden-verification {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--color-gray);
  }

  :global(.home-signup-form) {
    margin: var(--spacing-lg) 0;
  }

  a {
    color: var(--color-accent-teal);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>
